%F A142599 Sum_{n>=1} 1/a(n) = 5*Pi/(24*sqrt(3)) + 1/2. - _Amiram Eldar_, Sep 11 2022
%F A142599 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Jun 25 2026: (Start)
%F A142599 G.f.: x*(5 + 2*x + 77*x^2 + 35*x^3 + 206*x^4 + 14*x^5 + 206*x^6 + 38*x^7 + 77*x^8 + 2*x^9 + 5*x^10 - x^11) / (1 - x^4)^3.
%F A142599 a(n) = 3*a(n-4) - 3*a(n-8) + a(n-12) for n > 12. (End)
%t A142599 A061037[n_] := Numerator[(n-2)*(n+2)/(4*n^2)]; Table[A061037[n], {n, 1, 300}][[3 ;;  ;; 3]] (* _G. C. Greubel_, Sep 19 2018 *)
